overview: Alberto received his degree in Computer Science from Universidad Catolica Andres Bello in his native country of Venezuela. Since then he has worked with several successful start-ups, the first being Smart Realtor, where he developed an online system for real estate agents to publish and manage properties that is still used by over 2,000 agents in Latin America today. He has also created several successful mobile applications including some for the Blackberry smart phone, one of which currently has more than 50,000 active users daily (dolarbb.com). Most recently he cofounded Babalah, Evidente, and Pixable. He is currently the CTO at Pixable.
